cwe_id;
severity2;
cve_summaryspring-web is vulnerable to Reflected File Download &#x28;RFD&#x29; attack. An incomplete fix of CVE-2015-5211 allows an attacker to bypass the protection against RFD attack via the &#x60;jsessionid&#x60; path parameter.&#xa;&#xa;;

